Specifically, Windows Terminal JSON scheme files from the upstream
`windowsterminal/` directory are fetched, converted to OKLCH, and
republished. The upstream SHA used for each build is recorded in
`.upstream-sha` and embedded in every theme record (`upstreamSha` field).

All original authorship of individual color schemes remains with their
respective authors as attributed in the upstream repository.
